### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_token_aqui>
@dailyProductionId = <pega_el_id_de_la_produccion>
@dailyProductionExtraId = <pega_el_id_del_extra>
@customerId = <pega_el_id_del_cliente>
@deliveryId = <pega_el_id_del_delivery>
@extraProductId = <pega_el_id_del_extra_product>

### ─────────────────────────────
### DAILY PRODUCTIONS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Registrar producción diaria (ADMIN o EMPLOYEE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "production_date": "2026-06-16",
  "customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "delivery_id": "{{deliveryId}}",
  "traditional_qty": 8,
  "healthy_qty": 2,
  "vegetarian_qty": 0,
  "notes": "Entregar antes de las 12"
}

###

### Registrar producción sin delivery ni notas (ADMIN o EMPLOYEE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "production_date": "2026-06-16",
  "customer_id": "{{customerId}}",
  "traditional_qty": 4,
  "healthy_qty": 0,
  "vegetarian_qty": 1
}

###

### Listar producciones del día
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions?date=2026-06-16
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener producción por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/one?dailyProductionId={{dailyProductionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Actualizar producción (ADMIN o EMPLOYEE)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/{{dailyProductionId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "delivery_id": "{{deliveryId}}",
  "traditional_qty": 10,
  "healthy_qty": 3,
  "vegetarian_qty": 1,
  "notes": "Nota actualizada"
}

###

### ─────────────────────────────
### EXTRAS DE PRODUCCIÓN
### ─────────────────────────────

### Agregar extra a una producción (ADMIN o EMPLOYEE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/{{dailyProductionId}}/extras
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "extra_product_id": "{{extraProductId}}",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### Agregar otro extra a la misma producción
POST {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/{{dailyProductionId}}/extras
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "extra_product_id": "{{extraProductId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### Eliminar extra de una producción
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/{{dailyProductionId}}/extras/{{dailyProductionExtraId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─────────────────────────────
### TOTALES / CONSULTAS ESPECIALES
### ─────────────────────────────

### Totales de cocina del día (suma por tipo de menú)
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/totals/kitchen?date=2026-06-16
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Totales de extras del día (agrupados por producto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/daily-productions/totals/extras?date=2026-06-16
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
